data.description: This beautiful home features 2-story ceilings, and a 2-story foyer featuring a dramatic wood staircase. The kitchen opens to the Family room and the Breakfast room for ease of entertaining. All Bedrooms are located upstairs. The lovely Primary bedroom features an En-Suite with double sinks, a separate shower, a garden tub, and a walk-in closet. The Garage has been converted into a wonderful Flex Space that can be used as a Media Room, Bedroom, Game Room, or Study, hall bath has double sinks, plus a separate tub/shower room. Art niches and, a fabulous staircase. 2 blocks from elementary school, neighborhood park nearby.
